      "description": "This E46 M3 is a purist\u2019s specimen featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, renowned for its individual throttle bodies and high-revving 8,000 RPM redline. Mated to a crisp 6-speed Getrag manual transmission, the drivetrain is bolstered by a factory M-Variable limited-slip differential. This example has undergone critical preventative maintenance, including a comprehensive VANOS system overhaul and rear subframe reinforcement to ensure structural integrity under lateral load. The suspension maintains its signature MacPherson/multi-link geometry with refreshed bushings, preserving the communicative steering rack and 50/50 weight distribution. Mechanically sorted and ready for spirited driving.",
